hadiths[23]{hadithnumber,text}:
2862,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi bhi musalman ko layaq nahin ke uskey paas koi chiz ho jiskey mutalliq wo koi wasiyat karna chahta ho to wo do raaten bhi na guzaarey magar is haal mein ke uski wasiyat uskey paas likhi hui ho.''"
2863,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) koi Dinar , dirham ya oont , bakri nahin chhod gaey aur na kisi chiz ke mutalliq wasiyat hi farmaee."
2864,"Janab Aamir bin Saad apney walid ( Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo ( Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par) Makka mein bahut sakht bimar pad gaey yahan tak ke marney ke qarib ho gaey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey paas maal bahut hai aur eik beti ke alawa mera koi waris nahin, to kya main apna do tihai maal sadqa kar jaun? aapney farmaya : ''nahin.'' unhoney kaha : aadha maal? aapney farmaya : '' nahin .'' unhoney kaha : to eik tihai ? aapney farmaya : ''tihai ( kar saktey ho (aur eik tihai bhi ziyada hai. tumhara apney warison ko ghani chhod jana ziyada behtar hai is se ke unhen faqir chhod jao ke logon ke samney haath phelatey phiren . aur tum jo bhi kharch kartey ho to us par tumhen ajr aur sawab milta hai, yahan tak ke wo luqma jo tum apni biwi ke munh ki taraf uthatey ho (us par bhi tumhen sawab milta hai ).'' maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main apni hijrat se peechhey reh jaunga ? farmaya : ''agar tum merey baad peechhey reh bhi gaey to Allah ki raza ke liye jo bhi amal saleh karogey us se tumhara maqam aur darja buland hoga. aur shayad tum merey baad zinda rahogey yahan tak ke tum se eik qom faayda uthaey gi aur dusri nuqsan .'' phir farmaya : ''aey Allah ! merey as-haaba ki hijrat mukammal farma dey aur unhen unki ediyon par lauta na dey (Makka mein unki wafat na ho) lekin hasrat hai Saad bin Khaula par !'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un par afsos kar rahey they ke wo Makka mein wafat pa gaey they."
2865,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aapney farmaya : ''tu sadqa karey us haalat mein jabkey to sehat-mand ho, maal ka lalchi ho, zindagi ki umeed rakhta ho aur faqir ho janey ka khatkaa laga rehta ho. jo kuchh deney ka irada ho to us mein dheel na kar yahan tak ke jab jaan halaq mein aan atki to kehney lagey : falan ke liye itna hai aur falan ke liye itna , halanke wo falan ka ho chuka hai.'' ( virasat ki bina par) ."
2866,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan ka apni zindagi main eik dirham sadqa karna, maut ke waqt sau (dirham) sadqa kerney ki ba-nisbat ziyada afzal hai.''"
2867,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik insan mard ya aurat saath (60) saal tak Allah ki itaat ke amal kartey rehtey hain, phir jab unki maut ka waqt aata hai to wasiyat mein) warison ko) nuqsan dey jatey hain to unke liye aag wajib ho jati hai.'' (Shehar bin Hoshab ne) kaha : Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh par (من بعد وصية يوصى بها أو دين غير مضار . . .  ذلك الفوز العظيم) tak aayaat tilawat kin.'' wasiyat ya qarz ki adaegi ke baad jabkey wasiyat kerney waley ne nuqsan na pahunchaya ho ( wirsey ki taqseem ki jaey). ye Allah ka hukm hai aur Allah khoob ilm wala hausle wala hai. ye Allah ka hukm hai aur Allah khoob ilm wala hausle wala hai. ye haden hain Allah ki jo shakhs Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat kerega to usey Allah aisey baaghaat mein dakhil kerega jinkey nichey nehren behti hain. wo un mein hamesha rahega aur yehi azeem kamiyabi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : (is sanad mein) Ash'as bin Jabir, Nasr bin Ali ka dada hai."
2868,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha : ''aey Abu-Zar ! main tujhey kamzor paata hun, aur bila-shuba main terey liye wohi chiz pasand karta hun jo mujhey apney liye pasand hai, to kabhi do aadmiyon par bhi ameer na banna aur na kisi yateem ke maal ka wali banna.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ehale Misr is riwayat mein munfarid hain."
2869,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aayat ( إن ترك خيرا الوصية للوالدين والأقربين . ... . ) ''agar maal chhod jaey to maa baap aur qurbat daaron ke liye wasiyat karey.'' ka hukm ibtida (shuruat) mein aisey hi tha yahan tak ke isey aayat meeras ne mansookh kar diya.
2870,Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne har haq daar ko uska haq dey diya hai. isliye waris ke liye koi wasiyat nahin.''
2871,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan farmatey hain ke jab Shan Wale Allah ne ye aayaat utaari : (ولا تقربوا مال اليتيم إلا بالتي هي أحسن) ''yateem ke maal ke qarib mat jao magar achhey andaz se.'' aur (إن الذين يأكلون أموال اليتمى ظلما . .  . ۔) ''jo log zulm se yateemon ka maal khatey hain, wo apney peton mein aag bhar rahey hain aur an-qareeb wo dehakti aag mein jaeyngey.'' to jin logon ke yahan koi yateem tha unhoney uskey khaney peeney ko apney se juda kar diya. is tarah jo khana uska bacha rehta wo uskey liye rakh chhodtey yahan tak ke wo yateem hi usey khata ya kharab (aur zaya) ho jata. aur ye kaifiyat unke liye giraan hui aur unhoney iska tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kya, to Shan Wale Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : (ویسلونك an اليتمى قل إصلاح لهم خير وإن تخالطوهم فإخوانكم) ''ye log aap se yateemon ke baarey mein poochhtey hain. keh dijiye ke unki khair khuwahi behtar hai, agar tum unka maal apney maalon mein mila bhi lo to ye tumharey bhai hain.'' (Allah taala bad-niyat aur nek niyat her eik ko khoob janta hai.) chunanche un logon ne unka khana peena apney khaney peeney ke sath mila liya."
2872,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : main faqeer hun aur merey paas kuchh nahin hai aur merey yahan eik yateem bhi hai. to aapney farmaya : ''to apney yateem ke maal se kha sakta hai, lekin israaf aur fuzul kharchi ho, na jaldi kerney wala ho (ke uskey badey honey se pehley pehley uskey maal ko kharch kar daley) aur na uskey maal se to koi jama punji bananey wala ho.''"
2873,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye baat yaad rakhi hai : ''bulooghat ke baad yateemi nahin aur subah se raat tak khamosh rehna nahin.''
2874,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saat mohlik kamon se bacho.'' puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kon se hain? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ka shareek thehrana , jadu karna , jis jaan ko Allah ne mohtaram banaya hai usey qatl kar dalna siwaye uskey ke haq ke sath ho, sood khana , yateem ka maal harrap kar jana , jihad ke din (kafiron ka samna kerney sey) pusht pher kar chaley jana aur paak daman gunah se na-waqif momin aurton par tohmat lagana. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagrid ( Abul Ghais ka naam Salim hai jo ke ibn Mutee ka maula hai."
2875,"Janab Ubaid bin Umair apney walid se bayan kartey hain jo ke sahabi they, unhoney kaha ke eik shakhs ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kabeera gunah kya hain? aapney farmaya : '' wo nau (9) hain.'' aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur mazeed kaha : '' musalman maa baap ki nafarmani karna aur Baitullah Al-Haram ki be hurmati karna jo jeetey martey tumhara qibla hai.''"
2876,Hazrat Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Musab bin Umair (Raziallahu anhu) uhud ke roz Shahid ho gaey aur unke paas sirf eik dhaari daar chadar thi. ham jab us se unka sar dhaanptey to paon nangey ho jatey aur jab paon dhaanptey to sar nanga ho jata. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is se inka sar dhanp do aur paon par kuch izkhir ( ghaas ( dal do.''
2877,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kaha : maine eik londi apni walida ko sadqa di thi , walida faut ho gaee hai aur wo londi wirsey mein chhod gaee hai. aapney farmaya : ''tera sawab Sabit hua aur wo londi virasat mein tujhey wapis aa gaee.'' usney kaha : walida faut hui hai to us par eik mahiney ke rozey hain, agar main uski taraf se rozey rakhun to kya uski taraf se kifaayat ya qaza ho jaeygi ? aapney farmaya : ''haan !'' aurat ne kaha : walida ne hajj nahin kiya tha, agar main uski taraf se hajj karun to kya uski taraf se kifaayat ya qaza ho jaeygi? aapney farmaya : ''haan !''"
2878,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke) unke walid ( Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein kuchh zameen mili . wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir huey aur kaha : mujhey zameen mili hai aur is jaisa nafees maal mujhey kabhi nahin mila , to iskey baarey mein aap mujhey kya hukm detey hain? aapney farmaya : ''agar chaho to iskey asal ko apney paas rakho aur is ( ki aamdani ( ko sadqa kar do.'' chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne isko sadqa kar diya is shart ke sath ke iskey asal ko bechaa nahin jaeyga , hiba nahin kiya jaeyga aur na virasat hi mein wo taqseem hogi aur uski aamdani fuqaraa , qurbat daaron , gardanon ke chudaney , jihad aur musafiron ke liye kharch hogi .) Janab Musaddad ke ustaad ( Bishr ne ''mehmano ke liye'' bhi bayan kiya. aur iskey mutawalli par koi gunah nahin ke us ( aamdani ( mein se dastoor ke mutabiq khud khaye aur dost ko khilaaey , lekin maal jama kerney wala na ho. ( Janab Musaddad ke ustaad ( Bishr ne kaha : Muhammad (bin Aun (ke alfaz hain (غير متأثل مالا) (yani ''maal jama kerney wala na ho.'')"
2879,"Janab Yahya bin Saeed ne Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sadqa ( waqf (ke mutalliq bayan kya aur kaha : mujhey ye tehreer unke padpotey Abdul-Hamid bin Abdullah bin Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab ne naqal karkey di : ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ye tehreer Allah ke bandey umr ne Samagh wali jaaidaad ke baarey mein likhi hai. aur mazkura baala riwayat Naafe ki manind bayan ki, us mein tha ke '' mutawalli maal jama kerney wala na ho. uskey lafz they (غير متأثل مالا) aur jo phal zayed rahey to wo sawaliyon aur nadaron ka haq hai aur pura qissa bayan kya, kaha : aur agar Samagh ka mutawalli chahey to uskey phal (aamdani) se kaam-kaaj ke liye ghulam bhi kharid sakta hai. aur) eik dusri tehreer usko ( muaiqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) ne qalam band kya aur Janab Abdullah bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne gawahi di : ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ye wasiyat nama hai jo Allah ke bandey , ameerul-momeneen umr ki taraf se hai ke agar merey sath koi hadisa pesh aa jaey ( wafat pa jaun ( to Samagh aur Sirma bin Akwa wali jaaidaad aur wo ghulam jo wahan hain aur khaibar ( ki ghanimat se hasil honey ( waley so hissey aur us mein jo ghulam hain aur wo so hissey jo Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wadi ( qar ( mein) apney ehle ke) kharch ikhrajat ke liye chhodey hain unki mutawalli ( ummul-momenin ( Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) hongi jab tak ye hayaat rahen . unke baad unke ehle mein se sahibur-raey uskey mutawalli hongey aur shart ye hai ke us jaaidaad ko becha nahin jaeyga, kharida nahin jaeyga . mutawalli apni samajh ke mutabiq sawaaliyon , naadaaron aur qurbat daaron mein kharch kerega . aur uskey mutawalli par koi harj nahin ke khud khaye aur) aaney janey waley mehmano ko) khilaaey ya ghulam khareedey ."
2880,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' insan jab faut ho jata hai to teen soorton ke ilawa uskey sab amal ka silsila kat jata hai) aur wo ye hain : ( jari rehney wala sadqa , wo ilm jis se nafa uthaya jata rahey aur nek aulad jo uskey liye dua karti rahey .''"
2881,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri walida achcha wafat pa gaee hai. agar ye soorat na hoti (aur usey moqa milta ( to wo zarur koi sadqa kar jati aur koi Atiya deti . agar main uski taraf se sadqa karun to kya uski taraf se kifaayat hogi ? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan ! tum uski taraf se sadqa karo .''
2882,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ( Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri walida wafat pa gaee hai, agar main uski taraf se sadqa karun to kya usko nafa hoga ? aapney farmaya : haan ! to usney kaha : '' mera eik khajuron ka baagh hai, to aap gawah rahen ke maine usey apni walida ki taraf se sadqa kar diya hai.''"
2883,"Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Aas bin Waael ne wasiyat ki ke uski taraf se so gardanen ( ghulam ( azad kiye jaeyn . chunanche uskey bete Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski taraf se pachas ghulamon ko azad kya phir uskey bete Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski taraf se baqi pachas ghulamon ko azad karna chaha to kaha : main ( pehley ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kar lun , to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey baap ne so gardanen azad kerney ki wasiyat ki hai aur) merey bhai ( Hisham ne uski taraf se pachas ghulam azad kar diye hain aur pachas uskey zimmey baqi hain. to kya main uski taraf se azad kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo musalman hota aur tum uski taraf se ghulam azad kartey ya sadqa kartey ya uski taraf se hajj kartey to usko pahunch jata .''"
2884,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke uskey walid ( Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) faut ho gaey aur unke zimmey eik yahudi ka tees wasq qarz tha. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se mohlat talab ki magar usney inkar kar diya. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye taake yahudi ke yahan uski sifarish farma den , pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur yahudi se baat ki ke us qarz ke badley khajoor ka phal ley lo magar wo na maana , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se kaha ke mohlat dey do to bhi usney inkar kya. aur hadees bayan ki ."
